::Autofire::

Autofire growls as the Terrorsaur's shot hits his side, sending him into a 
small spin. He corrects his course, firing his shoulder cannon at Terrorsaur. 
He spins again as he sees DrillBit firing at him, the shots missing him by an 
inch as Autofire returns fire with his chainguns.
